Content:
Jawahar Navodaya vidyalya, Jaipur (  , ) is CBSE affiliated school of District Jaipur under Jaipur region of Navodaya Vidyalaya Samiti (NVS).One of 557 JNVS known for its academics, spread all over India by Government of India. Its located near Kotputali on NH 8(Jaipur-Delhi Highway),in just middle of nature. Jawahar Navodaya Vidyalaya, Jaipur is located near the village Paota in the Jaipur district. This school is residence school and all facilities to the students is free of cost from everyday needs to all educational needs. This school established in a temporary site in 1986 under 1986 education policy. Now school has buildings for all the purposes, school building, hostels, staff quarters, Multi-purpose hall. There is a Rajiv Smriti Van in the very center of the school which adds to its bio-diversity. A local seasonal river passes through Rajiv Smriti Van. In evening many glow-worms covers the way of the river and adds to its beauty. The elliptical area of Rajiv Smriti Van is surrounded by the road which two bridges to cross the river. This road connects all the buildings like Academic block, Staff quarters, Hostels, Mess and Playground with each other. Everything looks well planned;it also follows the same architecture as of most JNVs. JNV Jaipur have awarded the status of the Smart School in Jaipur Region. This Smart Status is given to Top Ten Schools of India. The entrance test for admission into 6th and 9th class of Jawahar Navodaya Vidyalaya, Paota is being conducted by the Navodaya Vidyalaya Samiti. The school syllabus is CBSE pattern. There are classes being conducted from 6th standard to 12th standard. Music, Computer science and SUPW are taught as optional subjects. The school has a computer room equipped with Internet and a music room with most of the instruments available. This Navodaya Vidyalaya comes under Homi J. Bhabha cluster in Jaipur region of Navodaya Vidyalaya Samiti (NVS). Under migration scheme the 30% students of 9th class migrated to JNV, Aliabada, Jamnagar, Gujarat. Third language is accordingly Gujarati Jawahar Navodaya Vidyalaya, Paota, Distrcit- Jaipur PIN- 303106, Rajasthan
